{"tid":2306661,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"Dear Jane 新大碟《Limerence》入邊嘅英文歌有驚喜","createTime":"2020-11-30T14:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T17:07:37.000Z","uid":371872,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a4c93ac5486e02c5518090144567e813bda1f81","tid":2306661,"uid":371872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vPu0kg8MnhY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvPu0kg8MnhY&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xLM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=932ce663\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vPu0kg8MnhY</a><br />\nDear Jane 2020年度專輯《Limerence》<br />\n12.3 各大音樂平台上架<br />\n<br />\n「Limerence」<br />\n&mdash;&mdash; 有愛到瘋狂，愛到不能自拔的意思，通常用作形容迷戀到無法控制的狀態。<br />\n<br />\nDear Jane 最新專輯「Limerence」所說的正是這一種愛到瘋狂，愛到極致的愛情。<br />\n專輯收錄11首歌曲，以情歌為題，紀錄11種不同方式的愛情，完美呈現愛情最極致的模樣。由愛情萌芽、熱戀、分歧、失戀，直到放下再重新出發，都一一紀錄當中。<br />\n01/ 最後一間唱片舖 <br />\n02/ 給防護罩一吻(feat. SOPHY) <br />\n03/ 銀河修理員 <br />\n04/ 哀的美敦書 <br />\n05/ Can&rsquo;t keep going on <br />\n06/ Make Me Stay <br />\n07/不明來電 <br />\n08/ 朋友區 <br />\n09/ 未開始已經結束 <br />\n10/ Just Another Night In Central Euphoria<br />\n11/ 世上唯一雙細胞 <br />\n<br />\nLink: <br />\n<a href=\"https://dearjane.lnk.to/Limerence_HighlightIL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdearjane.lnk.to%2FLimerence_HighlightIL&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xLM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=6259eea8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://dearjane.lnk.to/Limerence_HighlightIL</a><br />\n<br />\n#Limerence"},{"pid":"aa18a0fece3113d114b98aa278e7a548e7497d93","tid":2306661,"uid":366190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T16:14:45.000Z","msg":"我覺得有翻d xoxo既feel"},{"pid":"09f9945e69a1cb49b85edbc00865d69a68feb7a4","tid":2306661,"uid":371872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa18a0fece3113d114b98aa278e7a548e7497d93","tid":2306661,"uid":366190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T16:14:45